implantation bleeding when will happen exactly is it more or one two drops once an egg is fertilized it makes its way down into the uterus where it will implant itself and begin to grow this process is called implantation implantation takes days from beginning to end at the end of the process there may be implantation bleeding implantation bleeding happens when the egg is burrowing itself into the uterine wall a woman may notice some spotting implantation bleeding is more like spotting that happens off and on for a day maybe two if it is heavier or longer than that it's not implantation bleeding it is usually light pinkish or brownish in color most pregnant women do not experience implantation bleeding but if it does occur it happens about a week before your period is due hope this helps good luck Pregnancy Menstrual cycle Miscarriage Endometriosis Ectopic pregnancy Endometrium Obstetrics Emergency contraception Twin Abortion In vitro fertilisation Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Human cloning Sexual reproduction Fertility awareness Ovulation Childbirth Ovary Endometrial cancer Progesterone Puberty Oral contraceptive Embryo transfer Infertility Ovarian cancer Fertilisation Urinary incontinence Vaginal bleeding Xenomorph Pregnancy (mammals) Gonorrhoea Female reproductive system (human) Gynecologic hemorrhage Intrauterine device Polycystic ovary syndrome Premature birth Stroke Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Fetal development Placental abruption Human development Diabetic retinopathy Estrus cycle Stoat Hysterectomy Sea Otter Breastfeeding Prostate cancer Dysfunctional uterine bleeding Pearl Birth control Hearing impairment Mammalian embryogenesis Androgen insensitivity syndrome Adverse effect (medicine) Hydatidiform mole Obstetrical hemorrhage Stem cell Gynaecology Swyer syndrome Egg (biology) Ion implantation Scientology beliefs and practices Sexual intercourse Ascariasis Traumatic brain injury Placenta praevia Human sexual response cycle Radiation poisoning Space Marines